  "text": "Consequently techniques have emerged to speed up the training process such as batch normalisation [CITATION_1] that seeks to balance the signal distribution throughout the network, adaptive gradient balancing such as ADAM [CITATION_2] that seeks to balance the gradient signal directly, and weight normalisation [CITATION_3] that seeks to balance the weights in the convolutional filters to balance the signal strength.",
